              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Photoshop\n\n500 menu items and buttons\n\nYou use about 20\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 3,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "### 500 - 20 = 480\n\n**Everyone Tax**\n\nYou pay cognitive load for 480 features you'll never use."
            }
          ]
        }
