          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Problem #2: Application Boundaries\n\nYour thought doesn't stop at app edges. But your tools do.\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "**Traditional workflow:**\n- Research in browser\n- Switch to spreadsheet (context breaks)\n- Switch to doc (another restart)\n\nThree apps. Three cognitive restarts.\n\n**Your thinking breaks at application boundaries.**"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
