              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Three Transformations\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "**From Static to Breathing**\nNot fixed artifacts — surfaces that materialize and dissolve\n\n**From Application-Centric to Intent-Centric**\nNot \"which app?\" — \"what am I trying to understand?\"\n\n**From Interruption to Flow**\nYour thought doesn't break at boundaries"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
