              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "### Ephemeral Interfaces\n\nTransient cognitive surfaces—materializing around intent, adapting as understanding deepens, dissolving once their purpose is fulfilled."
