          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Characteristic 1: Purpose-Driven Lifecycle\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "**Traditional:**\n- You pay a bill\n- Form stays open\n- You close it manually\n\n**Ephemeral:**\n- You pay a bill\n- Payment form appears (pre-filled)\n- You confirm\n- Payment processes\n- **Interface dissolves**\n\nNot because 60 seconds passed.\nBecause the purpose was fulfilled."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
