              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 3,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Purpose-Driven, Not Timer-Based\n\n```dart\n// ❌ WRONG: Timer-based\nif (minutesSinceInteraction > 5) {\n  vanish();\n}\n\n// ✅ RIGHT: Purpose-driven\nif (taskCompleted) {\n  dissolve();\n}\nif (contextChanged && !relevantAnymore) {\n  fade();\n}\n```\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false
            }
