            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "**Multi-dimensional understanding:**\n- **Who** you are (skills, goals, expertise)\n- **Where** you are (environment, device)\n- **What** you're doing (task, progress)\n- **When** it's happening (time, urgency)\n\nSame capability. Different context. Different interface."
